title: Giving Money to Random Listeners
description:
Jeremy asks Lauren "Are You Smarter Than A 5th Grader" questions, and gives away money each time she answers correctly.

Leave a comment on Episode 28 of our YouTube channel (http://wildtil9.co/YouTube-Giveaway) with your Instagram or Twitter handle to let us know you're down to receive some money.

Go to DailyHarvest.com and enter promo code WILD to get twenty-five dollars off your first box!
Use our link so you can get three extra months free at ExpressVPN.com/WILD9.
Find your forever pieces at jennikayne.com and get 15% off your first order when you use code WILD at checkout.
Get 15% off your Brüush toothbrush kit and refill plan when you use promo code WILD at bruush.com
Get your SoulCycle at-home bike TODAY by visiting MySoulCycleBike.com/WILD, and use promo code WILD to get a free pair of at-home Select cycling shoes with your purchase.
Learn more about your ad choices. Visit podcastchoices.com/adchoices
